content.p:
Recalls paragraphs VIII.74
Official Records of the General Assembly, Eightieth Session, Supplement No. 7 (A/80/7). and VIII.96
A/80/7/Add.9. of the reports of the Advisory Committee, and requests the Secretary-General to enhance functional reporting between the information and communications technology Chiefs of United Nations entities and the Office of Information and Communications Technology, in a manner that complements and fully respects existing reporting mechanisms, and avoiding the creation of parallel or isolated structures, and update the General Assembly in the context of its next report on the information and communications technology strategy;
